<br />
<br />What we are discussing in this thread (and several others) is mapper capability above and beyond what is currently offered by any of those products / projects.
<br />
<br />Not that I am terribly concerned with it all, I just want a cart that I can plug into USB to load my ROMs on that supports MMC1 (or MMC3, or UNROM, or FME7, or whatever).

		

